陪你入去買好唔好阿? <br />\n(心諗反正你講廣東話咁正 你唔係呃我既 2蚊我買包糖仔請你食點話)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔係阿 我幫人買嫁 而家找錢少左2蚊阿 如果少左我會比人打嫁 可唔可以借2蚊比我阿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁我陪你入去問多次先好唔好阿? <br />\n<br />\n(已經有D失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但若然問左老闆真係岩岩係入面買完野跌左既 果2蚊我照比你喇)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔洗啦 果2蚊你比我啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 去左問先啦 我陪你入去喇 <br />\n<br />\n然後我講完呢句 開始行去多士果度<br />\n佢講左句 唔得阿 就向另一邊走左<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n唉 有D失望 <br />\n我返工有D都識講廣東語既南亞 同佢地講野都好nice<br />\n有時覺得識講廣東語既南亞都叫融入左我地 幫下手無乜所謂<br />\n點解你咁細個就要呃人呢小南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"係樓豬你咁豬先信呢D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係完全唔會信佢地講既任何野<br />\n衰撚過共慘黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749b5039bcd5cf749407ddc083e8b03f44b05ddc","tid":708692,"uid":169027,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"香港人都會咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次旺角地鐵站有個女人走黎話唔見左銀包<br />\n想我借錢俾佢返屋企<br />\n唔記得左佢起初問我攞幾錢 好似$40<br />\n佢話會還返俾我<br />\n我心諗唉算啦唔 都係$40姐 <br />\n跟住我攞銀包出黎 之後佢突然話未食野好肚餓 可唔可以要$100<br />\n我心諗唔好玩啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪咁似水魚 最後都俾左$50佢<br />\n佢都交足戲問我攞電話號碼 跟住寫都無寫 頭也不回就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人有時就無咁軟弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff1ab810f903190aeceda825f6f5741e8cc7b58","tid":708692,"uid":59114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"南亞人冇一個喺無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一喺就搶野一喺就強姦<br />\n再唔喺就兩樣都喺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a355f652ca5e5855dc198119fe5b7c9082e87085","tid":708692,"uid":74629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"樓主心地好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ba433944301e14805b276aa974752b8da57813","tid":708692,"uid":126720,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"有時見到啲講廣東話既係街到請我幫手都會幫下。但可唔可以唔好呃人吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到而家完全唔敢幫人⋯⋯香港人冷漠係比呢班呃人既仆街呃岀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cbdeee17886bb067c28cb5f4063ce945ce0535","tid":708692,"uid":32279,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"一生生幾個 跟住幾家住埋附近<br />\n然後放學3，2個老母傾計<br />\n之後成7-8個蝻喺度走黎走去<br />\n撞到人唔理 亂尻咁黎<br />\n上次放狗好地地啲男蝻走黎想踢我隻狗<br />\n即刻屌佢老母同佢講我隻狗會咬死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f50375d180df32f5d747e73004b5c9ee5bfa57f","tid":708692,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"749b5039bcd5cf749407ddc083e8b03f44b05ddc","tid":708692,"uid":169027,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"香港人都會咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次旺角地鐵站有個女人走黎話唔見左銀包<br />\n想我借錢俾佢返屋企<br />\n唔記得左佢起初問我攞幾錢 好似$40<br />\n佢話會還返俾我<br />\n我心諗唉算啦唔 都係$40姐 <br />\n跟住我攞銀包出黎 之後佢突然話未食野好肚餓 可唔可以要$100<br />\n我心諗唔好玩啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪咁似水魚 最後都俾左$50佢<br />\n佢都交足戲問我攞電話號碼 跟住寫都無寫 頭也不回就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人有時就無咁軟弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:34:39.000Z","msg":"幾時借比我？"},{"pid":"e6edec1b8c514055e8fb9a712fb0f8c274e3c73d","tid":708692,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"香港人都大把哩d，關咩事"},{"pid":"760a4cce9960fc03c8ebd56c7a174087803b5b10","tid":708692,"uid":29093,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"小南亞:「依家啲毒撚 越嚟越聰明架啦」"},{"pid":"caeaa386e6508194316d39ea10b4ff93c6f4fcb6","tid":708692,"uid":12597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"幾年前借咗20蚊比個蝻仔搭車<br />\n而家諗返都覺得自己on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353c68c51505fc65ff8933313d9c456c2cf129e3","tid":708692,"uid":74980,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"你又知佢8歲？<br />\n從你打出黎嘅對話佢都無講過自己幾歲喎"},{"pid":"6896084f1569ffcb41982f2ed476701e572790b1","tid":708692,"uid":476,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:49:42.000Z","msg":"不嬲比錢任何陌生人當買旗<br />\n佢地話用黎搭車你真係信呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無分人種 問得陌生人拎銀仔這個行為本身已經係乞兒"},{"pid":"c6c8ade711c284ffb46e337c606200e4266a9fd9","tid":708692,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"974df59085b5549897e973d37d8469e4cc72d2b8","tid":708692,"uid":115773,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:13:08.000Z","msg":"屌你2蚊比人啦, 呃你2蚊洗死咩"},{"pid":"2412dece39b9d7577bfab205a0f51760a472bdf8","tid":708692,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"試過有阿伯話口渴問我攞廿蚊買烏龍茶<br />\n我又真係比左佢，事後諗返，口渴買水啦，飲乜鳩烏龍茶，仲洗撚廿蚊，諗返都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed59406e22174a17e7129cdbef73b40a3ae2f5e2","tid":708692,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:23:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cdb432b27a541ee90e67245f2551a3828ceaae5","tid":708692,"uid":167219,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"我都試過<br />\n屋企樓下有南亞細路問我借廿蚊搭返屋企<br />\n只係一個地鐵站既距離<br />\n我話搭返去唔駛咁多錢架喎<br />\n佢即刻收左話十蚊就得<br />\n其實個刻都知佢呃我既<br />\n但都會諗會唔會真係需要我幫<br />\n我話陪佢去搭車幫佢俾錢<br />\n佢即刻話唔駛就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdb82772f33add87e7b76569f65c88aad6299ec","tid":708692,"uid":147242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:24:36.000Z","msg":"無一個係無辜"},{"pid":"c6fa6bfc361304ff9736b3ab994bb2620f398e82","tid":708692,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:26:03.000Z","msg":"其實佢呃2蚊真係算良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前試過廢老借錢搭車黨<br />\n明明一個站車程地鐵站就係正隔離<br />\n但一開口就要借20蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻收返埋銀包，第二日又見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後舊登都有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53615510922a47ec29b2a287c840c903705b80b","tid":708692,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"南亞人都會有nice既 但唔會係香港果啲囉 黎得香港都死窮撚啦 呃唔到你總會有下一隻水魚"},{"pid":"76a106066859c5d9523e0e564c7f57bfadd58944","tid":708692,"uid":77383,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:32:40.000Z","msg":"我住係天水圍<br />\n以前細個會儲埋儲埋啲報紙拎去樓下收賣佬賣<br />\n賣到嗰少少錢可以返學校買媽咪麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁通常緊係儲埋一大堆再疊埋係架拉車仔先拎去賣<br />\n對一個嗰時得14歲既女仔黎講架車仔真係好重<br />\n咁有一次行到一半過馬路<br />\n架車仔個轆爛左<br />\n啲報紙跌哂落地下散開哂<br />\n好彩嗰時無車經過但係都搞到好狼狽<br />\n我執執下然後就有一對父子南亞黎幫我執<br />\n疊返好仲幫我放返係架車仔度<br />\n最後佢兩個仲一個拎頭一個拎尾咁拎起我架好重既車仔<br />\n拎到去收賣佬度就頭也不回走左<br />\n得人因果千年記<br />\n佢地真係好好人<br />\n呢件事我記到今時今日<br />\n我信香港仲會有0.5%既南亞係好人<br />\n不過唔知過咁左多年佢地有冇變左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3fe50fe3be8f65f4434d0448487c15d30cdc12","tid":708692,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fbc36cccf3fc2d93cbe9bc259186d0e0671729","tid":708692,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"全部蝻都係社會垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e7f26caa4118f637352aa9301d98db68a840bc","tid":708692,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n之後有兩個蝻<br />\n太約10-12歲<br />\n問我借10蚊雞搭車<br />\n之後過兩日<br />\n又係樓下撞到佢兩個<br />\n係咁問人借錢搭車<br />\n個時先知佢兩個根本就住係到<br />\n日日搵水魚"},{"pid":"2128478e3242f49d83a0f5d2ed9dbb0b9e4028e5","tid":708692,"uid":154180,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"老實講我覺得樓主個應對好好<br />\n下下都防範人好辛苦<br />\n佢有個方法大機會確認到個細路係咪呃佢就ok啦"},{"pid":"707a5773bf8dd675b38eb28cc0d3ac946be38547","tid":708692,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2e7f26caa4118f637352aa9301d98db68a840bc","tid":708692,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n之後有兩個蝻<br />\n太約10-12歲<br />\n問我借10蚊雞搭車<br />\n之後過兩日<br />\n又係樓下撞到佢兩個<br />\n係咁問人借錢搭車<br />\n個時先知佢兩個根本就住係到<br />\n日日搵水魚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:45:03.000Z","msg":"我住黃大仙區 好近黃大仙地鐵站<br />\n各位街坊小心"},{"pid":"07817a1d272d9addcd073d1562c05d96b15206a6","tid":708692,"uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"353c68c51505fc65ff8933313d9c456c2cf1