r />\n但都會諗會唔會真係需要我幫<br />\n我話陪佢去搭車幫佢俾錢<br />\n佢即刻話唔駛就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T20:48:21.000Z","msg":"你真係知佢呃你？！<br />\n咁你仲俾錢佢咪啫係助長咗啲蝻亞狗呃人囉<br />\n講嘢用把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做嘢用個腦啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T21:33:05.000Z","msg":"你邊隻眼見到我話俾左錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4ac22ea3e3d64e627b1ca9c550329d22adf106","tid":708692,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T22:18:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾始終係垃圾，樓主呢d大愛左膠注定要受懲罰"},{"pid":"acd1d1341a4e8e7024d3b3ea4975054f58c202cb","tid":708692,"uid":180984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T22:22:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72061fb8aa82833a361a5d18dd224ea30c7fcb02","tid":708692,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccf5f9fc871c904f9d82b9667f67feaa98ba9e31","tid":708692,"uid":32699,"like":43,"dislike":68,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攬住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T22:42:13.000Z","msg":"痛你老母   可憐d賤畜"},{"pid":"392cb403d26ea7afc8afa658b6b002a536cbeb38","tid":708692,"uid":39376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T22:44:30.000Z","msg":"中一個陣同同學放學漏左銀包係學校 跑翻去拎個陣跌埋電話 翻到去又搵唔到銀包 之後先發現跌埋電話 翻去711搵個同學 個同學又走左去 <br />\n之後我一路行一路喊 有一家人好好心問我咩事 之後俾左電話我打翻屋企 再俾左廿蚊我撘車 我到而家都仲記得 好多謝個家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81f5e90a8165b997d8e05a544f82ffbce9fd726","tid":708692,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T23:07:34.000Z","msg":"賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e365a8d5114ca30a5d01bcea1ce33f0eb4c0c8","tid":708692,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,