5965d629d79","tid":708692,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:52:09.000Z","msg":"低等生物就係低等生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d4adf1431e4230b1a1580b64a8240cf52e53f6","tid":708692,"uid":72735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"其實所有呢啲野你諗真d就會覺得唔合理<br />\n有咩理由要借錢搭車<br />\n<br />\n連一個朋友都搵唔到嚟救你？<br />\n跌左銀包唔去差館報失？<br />\n冇錢搭車的話可以行路<br />\n過海嘅同巴士司機講下次比返又得<br />\n<br />\n街邊鬼佬帶住個仔，棟個牌寫住唔見晒護照銀包果d又係<br />\n你唔去差館/領事館，坐係度問人攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f28a6acf02558ebd7eb03f3db051bf1b0bc2514","tid":708692,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T01:18:33.000Z","msg":"細時偷針 大時偷金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bcc276b7a234b9e78569bc3ccadd2a2ddadf73","tid":708692,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"根本應該送佢地返原居地<br />\n<br />\n因乜收留佢地?<br />\n<br />\n都唔同種族"},{"pid":"6e66a1ecaf6876fd274fa82152124a59f59d5ed2","tid":708692,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"南亞同克羅地亞d小朋友一樣 除左乞仲會搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56eb8f86feeb5c1113463517dc2a7f630a8cd452","tid":708692,"uid":71303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:26:14.000Z","msg":"呢排都好興d大陸女遊客話無錢然後話俾少少錢佢食飯，又話之後還番又剩。上連登先知係騙子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b7c35fb9f16d1a2d6512915e541e6badfba038","tid":708692,"uid":165202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁撚大膽...細個嗰陣淨係夠膽係老豆褲袋到偷銀仔 一次起兩次止<br />\n究竟經歷左咩會令佢咁大膽係條街到呃人錢....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b0d794fbcefd88a12cc43483af987783cfb670","tid":708692,"uid":99607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"間唔時都有D講普通話嘅話無錢搭車 又話無錢食飯 <br />\n仆街嚟一個二個"},{"pid":"1529500b055d1a578afb7af09c8dc9e0756552fb","tid":708692,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f86b7be2c62bd3ccfbb657f23249d00a4aa9430c","tid":708692,"uid":102132,"like":111,"dislike":0,"score":111,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"Load左兩秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f696e4d7de7c63d1c3ad629422bc0b634003061","tid":708692,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d60093dd1fcdd5d7935c01cba64d049a152082e8","tid":708692,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"岩岩返到屋企樓下<br />\n有個8歲左右包頭巾既小南亞捧住D零食走埋黎<br />\n用無口音既廣東話問我借2蚊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 可唔可以借2蚊比我阿?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 做咩阿?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我岩岩係間士多買野 跌左個2蚊係入面 個老闆話無阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁我陪你入去買好唔好阿? <br />\n(心諗反正你講廣東話咁正 你唔係呃我既 2蚊我買包糖仔請你食點話)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔係阿 我幫人買嫁 而家找錢少左2蚊阿 如果少左我會比人打嫁 可唔可以借2蚊比我阿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁我陪你入去問多次先好唔好阿? <br />\n<br />\n(已經有D失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但若然問左老闆真係岩岩係入面買完野跌左既 果2蚊我照比你喇)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔洗啦 果2蚊你比我啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 去左問先啦 我陪你入去喇 <br />\n<br />\n然後我講完呢句 開始行去多士果度<br />\n佢講左句 唔得阿 就向另一邊走左<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n唉 有D失望 <br />\n我返工有D都識講廣東語既南亞 同佢地講野都好nice<br />\n有時覺得識講廣東語既南亞都叫融入左我地 幫下手無乜所謂<br />\n點解你咁細個就要呃人呢小南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:45:42.000Z","msg":"個種個基因植入左"},{"pid":"aee5d1f2f4c59c3dca80782552ebbcc58e7c09c4","tid":708692,"uid":132335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"屌 琴日係尖沙咀地鐵站又係有呢啲細路問我借10蚊<br />\n我話冇 <br />\n點知轉個頭佢啲包頭蝻狗 攞錢比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0cd9f87d16c9edfe4f9f483493dc469202449c","tid":708692,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"俾左$100 佢[/s]"},{"pid":"181c536889fed15ce6b2a5da7996d1d1829848e5","tid":708692,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c63b6b999c292e288cf38c6eca68970f6ef77b4c","tid":708692,"uid":27960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ddc5ef61e3d5fd3e84e185ff36318ed7e3dc45","tid":708692,"uid":167219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f75e98dc47d222c46d30e57397cebd33728d0eaa","tid":708692,"uid":27960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4cdb432b27a541ee90e67245f2551a3828ceaae5","tid":708692,"uid":167219,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"我都試過<br />\n屋企樓下有南亞細路問我借廿蚊搭返屋企<br />\n只係一個地鐵站既距離<br />\n我話搭返去唔駛咁多錢架喎<br />\n佢即刻收左話十蚊就得<br />\n其實個刻都知佢呃我既<br />\n但都會諗會唔會真係需要我幫<br />\n我話陪佢去搭車幫佢俾錢<br />\n佢即刻話唔駛就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T20:48:21.000Z","msg":"你真係知佢呃你？！<br />\n咁你仲俾錢佢咪啫係助長咗啲蝻亞狗呃人囉<br />\n講嘢用把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做嘢用個腦啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T21:33:05.000Z","msg":"你邊隻眼見到我話俾左錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:06:22.000Z","msg":"而家係人地走咗<br />\n唔係你知佢呃你所以你走喎"},{"pid":"b6efa4a9000844aea0edff5d606eeff857603701","tid":708692,"uid":1188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:27:14.000Z","msg":"你點知佢8歲？<br />\n<br />\n點解成個post都無人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2650c78a33955281238851eee65e3d73e0860388","tid":708692,"uid":166986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"749b5039bcd5cf749407ddc083e8b03f44b05ddc","tid":708692,"uid":169027,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"香港人都會咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次旺角地鐵站有個女人走黎話唔見左銀包<br />\n想我借錢俾佢返屋企<br />\n唔記得左佢起初問我攞幾錢 好似$40<br />\n佢話會還返俾我<br />\n我心諗唉算啦唔 都係$40姐 <br />\n跟住我攞銀包出黎 之後佢突然話未食野好肚餓 可唔可以要$100<br />\n我心諗唔好玩啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪咁似水魚 最後都俾左$50佢<br />\n佢都交足戲問我攞電話號碼 跟住寫都無寫 頭也不回就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人有時就無咁軟弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:47:23.000Z","msg":"我都遇過 話要去醫院 冇錢俾車錢 問我攞一百蚊 佢又話俾身份證 又電話號碼 咁我就信咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依完諗返起 好蠢啊我真係"},{"pid":"d47852397ebada5cfb1d8fe6448c965ce1eabfbb","tid":708692,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aff1ab810f903190aeceda825f6f5741e8cc7b58","tid":708692,"uid":59114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"南亞人冇一個喺無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一喺就搶野一喺就強姦<br />\n再唔喺就兩樣都喺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T22:35:02.000Z","msg":"巴打 你每做一件事都有報應架 <br />\n唔好亂咁歧視人。南亞人就生活係你身邊 你散播呢種仇視 只會增加大家既危險性 <br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你支持佢地 上面講左咩你自己參透下啦"},{"pid":"ba180c1f7fca76a4555bf88fd28dc180078895a6","tid":708692,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T22:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d956046265d1699448d2b26c07de12f829ccfc09","tid":708692,"uid":171594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T00:14:24.000Z","msg":"蝻條鳩好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a54125aee14e5f338d8e2f7a5469e67f123c7e","tid":708692,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T00:19:49.000Z","msg":"關人種鬼時，見過香港人同大陸人都用呢招"},{"pid":"1974730c7f78d7610d5d08d62aee0e370c14e114","tid":708692,"uid":167219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c63b6b999c292e288cf38c6eca68970f6ef77b4c","tid":708692,"uid":27960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ddc5ef61e3d5fd3e84e185ff36318ed7e3dc45","tid":708692,"uid":167219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f75e98dc47d222c46d30e57397cebd33728d0eaa","tid":708692,"uid":27960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T20:48:21.000Z","msg":"你真係知佢呃你？！<br />\n咁你仲俾錢佢咪啫係助長咗啲蝻亞狗呃人囉<br />\n講嘢用把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做嘢用個腦啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T21:33:05.000Z","msg":"你邊隻眼見到我話俾左錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:06:22.000Z","msg":"而家係人地走咗<br />\n唔係你知佢呃你所以你走喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T00:38:17.000Z","msg":"即係咁<br />\n呢個世界好多人係呃人但總有人真係有需要<br />\n所以先話陪佢去搭幫佢俾錢而唔係直接俾錢佢<br />\n真係需要個d有人幫佢俾錢點會話唔好<br />\n但如果係呃錢個d呃唔到現金仲哂時間咪會話唔好然後走囉<br />\n駁人前諗下人地做野個出發點係乜先啦<br />\n要人畫公仔畫出腸同你解釋點解要咁講要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}